profile: At Steam Dry Canada, our customers are our business. Whether it is our carpet, upholstery, area rug, furnace and duct cleaning, indoor air quality division or the flood rescue division, we strive to give our customers superior, detailed and precise results. Our service technicians will provide these superior services with integrity and sincere customer service. We don't send salespeople into our customers homes, we send qualified technicians that are focused on meeting and exceeding our customers expectations. We want to give our customers the most enjoyable in-home service that they have ever received and we are not satisfied until our customers are satisfied, guaranteed.

profile:
Our website:  http://www.customblindsplus.com

We bring our store to your door – contact us and we come to your home for a free in-home consultation.  What better way to ensure that you get the right product – custom window blinds and window shades including California shutters, cellular shades, pleated shades, cellular blinds, roller shades, wood blinds, roller blinds, venetian blinds, motorized blinds, vertical blinds and drapery  – that best fits your needs and design inspirations.

Custom Blinds Plus prides itself on its ability to provide its customers with quality, custom made, brand name blinds and window coverings at the Best Price available anywhere. As a proud member of Better Business Bureaus, as well as a member of Business Network International you can be assured that we are providing the best service in Ottawa. For references/recommendations please contact the appropriate organizations.

Our Best Price Policy ensures that you are getting the best value for your money. If at any time after you have placed your order with Custom Blinds Plus, and before the delivery and installation of the order, should you obtain a bona fide written quotation for the same blinds and window coverings at a lower price, Custom Blinds Plus will beat that quotation by a further 5%.
